description:
This week's Rusty Fears 5 winner is "Final Sale of the Remaining Works of E. Cutler" written by Cormack Baldwin, directed by Elizabeth Moffatt and performed by Imogen Harris.

Note: this is a piece of stand-alone fiction and not a part of the Magnus canon.

Content warnings:

  • Supernatural compulsion
  • Scopophobia
  • Death & murder
  • Discussions of: isolation & mental deterioration
  • Mentions of: cultural appropriation, spiders, religion & faith, blood, rot, suicide
  • SFX: low continuous drone, high pitched tones

Transcripts:

PDF - https://bit.ly/2Z3Y4iN

DOC - https://bit.ly/3vxwzcX
